name: Daniel Rey Cimafranca
text: Yup di dapat.  Just asking for details di ko kasi nasubaybayan.  So now unfortunately the burden is on whoever else has legal right to pursue the case since ayaw nung isa.  CHR siguro, trabaho naman nila yun.
